# Red Cabbage and Lentil Bowl

Based on [https://www.loveandlemons.com/buddha-bowl-recipe](https://www.loveandlemons.com/buddha-bowl-recipe) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260130002713/https://www.loveandlemons.com/buddha-bowl-recipe/))

